title: Quest's End
description: The Wolfriders have escaped the prison of Blue Mountain, but have gone from the frying pan into the fire. The Palace of the High Ones calls to them, but as they journey, they are set upon by ferocious trolls who guard the relic. Now the elves tend their wounds in the lodges of the Go-Backs and wonder... can any of them survive the First and Final War?
author: Wendy Pini
